chmod +x install-smart-sites.sh
./install-smart-sites.sh



⚠️ Important Notes After Running
	•	Reboot your Pi after the script finishes to apply Docker group permissions.
	•	Make sure you have already copied the full Smart Sites project into ~/SmartSites.
	•	Replace /dev/ttyUSB0 in the script if your Z-Wave dongle uses a different port.
	•	Access Z-Wave JS UI via a browser: http://<your-pi-ip>:8091